== Welcome to Gender Detector app

-- This is the Naive Bayes implementation of gender detection algorithm in Ruby on Rails.

The logic is written in 'bayes.rb' file which can be found in the app root directory.

References:

http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Naive_Bayes_classifier

Book followed: Ruby on Rails Tutorial Learn Rails by Example Michael Hartl.

Note:

It is important that the heights and weights are not given same values for all training examples,
because that will lead the variance to be zero and generate NaN values for "Normal Distribution"
calculation formula as given at wiki page.


--Arun Shyam